<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/914479-when-reading-mr-moundshroud-s-physical">When reading Mr. Moundshroud&#39;s physical description I felt sure that Tim Burton have read it before conceiving Jack Skellington. I suspect that the first may have been a inspiration for the second, but found nothing related to it on a quick google search. What do you think? Has anyone thought the same when reading the book?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_914479'><a id="like_count_community_question_914479" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/914479?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F761381.The_Halloween_Tree">like</a></span>

</li>
