<div id="review_2106676898" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2106676898" />
    <a title="Rachel Bea" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/2805400-rachel-bea"><img alt="Rachel Bea" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1526942660p2/2805400.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2106676898?book_show_action=true">Aug 17, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Rachel Bea" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Rachel Bea" href="/user/show/2805400-rachel-bea">Rachel Bea</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/25344096-the-halloween-tree">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2805400-rachel-bea?shelf=books-of-2018">books-of-2018</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2805400-rachel-bea?shelf=middle-grade">middle-grade</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2805400-rachel-bea?shelf=tower-teams-vi">tower-teams-vi</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2805400-rachel-bea?shelf=tcf2018">tcf2018</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2805400-rachel-bea?shelf=folk-horror">folk-horror</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2805400-rachel-bea?shelf=under-200-pages">under-200-pages</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2106676898" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5153284928917713292">Vivid<br/>Imaginative<br/>Fantastic<br/>Dark<br/><br/>...I think I could quote this book forever...<br/><br/><i>Night and day. Summer and winter, boys. Seedtime and harvest. Life and death. That’s what Halloween is, all rolled up in one. Noon and midnight. Being born, boys. Rolling over, playing dead like dogs, lads. And getting up again, barking, racing through thousands of years of death each day and each night Halloween, boys, every night, every single night dark and fearful until at last you made it and hid in cities and towns a</i></span>
  <span id="freeText5153284928917713292" style="display:none">Vivid<br />Imaginative<br />Fantastic<br />Dark<br /><br />...I think I could quote this book forever...<br /><br /><i>Night and day. Summer and winter, boys. Seedtime and harvest. Life and death. That’s what Halloween is, all rolled up in one. Noon and midnight. Being born, boys. Rolling over, playing dead like dogs, lads. And getting up again, barking, racing through thousands of years of death each day and each night Halloween, boys, every night, every single night dark and fearful until at last you made it and hid in cities and towns and had some rest and could get your breath.</i></span>
  <a data-text-id="5153284928917713292" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


