        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1798596805" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3969808499027415118">It was good, just not the Bradbury I’m accustomed to. Made me think about the origins of Halloween, which is the whole point. Best part by far came near the end – where meaningful Bradbury surfaced.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


